{
  "stem": "25773.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was in the small ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My whole family-- let's say, like my grandmother, my beloved auntie, and uncles, and cousins, and whatever, were in the big ghetto.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And even small-- my youngest brother, I secured-- because I couldn't secure for him any place-- my-- in the big ghetto.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, I would like to add that my stepbrother was taken-- you know--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He developed tuberculosis.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was with us, still in 1940, in our flat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he developed tuberculosis.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And with our very good old friend, a doctor, we managed-- particularly, because my parents wouldn't and be able to-- we managed to smuggle him out, outside the-- we were only in the ghetto, but it was not yet completely closed, you see?",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we smuggled him out to a place called Otvosk, which was on the same line as our little villa.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our villa was in [NON-ENGLISH], where we had the villa, and that was Otvosk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was known for-- there was no penicillin for curing tuberculosis, but it was-- pine tree were there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And lot of pine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The good air, and a sanatorium.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we smuggled him there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the kindly doctors and nurses accepting him, knowing, even knowing, that he was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK, we're coming now to the end of the first tape.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
